data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in Gold Creek Estates, a gated subdivision offering walking trails, pool/game area, clubhouse, fitness center and maintained front yard landscaping. Situated on a spacious corner lot with the Solar Owned*, this home offers a blend of elegance and modern comfort. The heart of the home is the open living room and kitchen/dining concept with an inviting gas log fireplace. The fully fenced backyard, accessible from the living area, provides a private oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Upstairs, you'll find 4 bedrooms offering ample space for the entire family. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary with its ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, a large soaking tub, and an expansive walk-in closet. The lower level hosts a versatile bonus room, perfect for a home office, gym, formal dining area or additional entertainment space. Elegant wood flooring graces the interior, complementing the modern and tasteful design of the guest bathrooms. Step outside to the landscaped backyard, complete with a beautiful flagstone patio, offering a perfect retreat for outdoor gatherings and room for gardening. Enjoy the 3rd car tandem garage door, a  unique addition providing convenient access & extra space, perfect for a workshop, or additional storage. Come see for yourself and Love where you Live! *Solar to be paid off by seller with an acceptable offer.
